# Gai Framework (github.com/Hlgxz/gai) — Go web framework LIBRARY
# Usage: gai new myapp → creates project with AI rules for all tools
# MUST: import gai/http as ghttp
# Handler: func(c *ghttp.Context) — c.Success(), c.Error()
# ORM: orm.Query[T](db), orm.Get[T](q), orm.Create[T](db, &item)
# Model: embed orm.Model, gai:"..." tags
# Route: r.Group(), r.Resource(), :param paths
# Middleware: c.Next() required
# Validate: pipe syntax required|email|min:5
# Schema: YAML → gai generate --schema
